    <!-- Question 1 -->
    <ReportSection id="q1" tooltip="Quiz" name="Quiz"  title="QUESTION 1" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection">
        <Static>
            <![CDATA[
                <script type="text/javascript">
                    dc.init(me.get('id'), 'Sleep');
                    dc.increment('quizPageCount');
                    dc.timer('quizTime');
                </script>
                <p>Now that you’ve read about the three main ingredients (or factors) involved in making changes to your behaviour, let's review and see how much you remember.</p>
            ]]>
        </Static>
        <ReportItem id="q1" type="Radio" blobItem="Q1" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" options="True|False">
            <![CDATA[
                <h3>It is normal for sleep to become more of a challenge as we age.</h3>
                {$item}
                <script type='text/javascript'>
                    dc.radio('q1', 'input[type=radio]');
                </script>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Answer 1 -->
    <ReportSection id="a1" tooltip="Answers1" name="Answer1" title="QUESTION 1" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q1" type="Answer" blobItem="Q1" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" label="Answer 1" answer="True">
            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <p>It’s normal to experience earlier bedtimes and earlier wake-up times, more sleep during the day, less sleep during the night, lighter sleep, and more awakenings during sleep.</p>
                <p>These changes may be normal, but they may not necessarily have an impact on your daily living. For some people, less sleep is required as they get older.</p>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Question 2 -->
    <ReportSection id="q2" tooltip="Quiz" name="Quiz2" title="QUESTION 2" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q2" type="Radio" blobItem="Q2" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" options="a. At least 30 minutes before bedtime|b. 4 to 6 hours before bedtime|c. 2 to 4 hours before bedtime|d. At least 6 hours before bedtime">
            <![CDATA[
                <h3>When should we have our last cup of coffee or favourite caffeinated drink?</h3>
                {$item}
                <script type='text/javascript'>
                    dc.radio('q2', 'input[type=radio]');
                </script>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Answer 2 -->
    <ReportSection id="a2" tooltip="Answers1" name="Answer2" title="QUESTION 2" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q2" type="Answer" blobItem="Q2" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" label="Answer 2" answer="b. 4 to 6 hours before bedtime">
            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <p>This will ensure there is no caffeine in your system causing you to toss and turn and unable to fall asleep.</p>
                
                <p>Reducing overall liquid intake before bed will help decrease the number of times you need to urinate throughout the night.</p>
                
                <p>Check out the resource library for more information on sleep.</p>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Question 3 -->
    <ReportSection id="q3" tooltip="Quiz" name="Quiz3" title="QUESTION 3" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q3" type="Radio" blobItem="Q3" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" options="a. Develop a consistent bedtime routine|b. Exercise during the day|c. Have a glass of wine right before you go to bed|d. Keep your room dark, quiet and cool">
            <![CDATA[
                <h3>What is not an example of a good sleep habit:</h3>
                {$item}
                <script type='text/javascript'>
                    dc.radio('q3', 'input[type=radio]');
                </script>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Answer 3 -->
    <ReportSection id="a3" tooltip="Answers1" name="Answer3" title="QUESTION 3" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q3" type="Answer" blobItem="Q3" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" label="Answer 3" answer="c. Have a glass of wine right before you go to bed">
            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <p>Alcohol can cause sleep disturbances, poorer quality of sleep, and may initiate another trip to the bathroom during the night.</p>
                <p>On the other hand, a consistent bedtime routine, exercise, and keeping a cool and quiet room for sleeping can all help with sleep quality.</p>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Question 4 -->
    <ReportSection id="q4" tooltip="Quiz" name="Quiz4" title="QUESTION 4" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
