            <![CDATA[
                <h3>Overall, good health is associated with better sleep.</h3>
                {$item}
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Answer 4 -->
    <ReportSection id="a4" tooltip="Answers1" name="Answer4" title="QUESTION 4" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q4" type="Answer" blobItem="Q4" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" label="Answer 4" answer="True">
            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <b>If you follow the AVOID Frailty components, good sleep will likely follow.</b>
                <p>Regular activity, making sure you see your doctor or pharmacist for annual medication reviews, keeping stress levels down, having someone to turn to for support and interaction, and being aware of timing regarding caffeine and alcohol can lead to better quality sleep.</p>
            ]]>
